Package com.cafean.client.ui.clipboard

Class ComponentCopier

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.client.ui.clipboard.ComponentCopier
  • public class ComponentCopier
extends java.lang.Object
    A utility class encapsulating the copying of components to the clipboard.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor Description
      ComponentCopier()
      Creates a new ComponentCopier for use in copying components, annotations and drawn components to the clipboard.

        public int getComponentCount()

      • addClipboardListener

        public static void addClipboardListener​(ClipboardListener listener)
        Adds the given listener to the table of listeners notified when a clipboard operation takes place.

        Note: Only one listener can be present for a particular plug-in. Adding multiple listeners will simply remove the first.

        Parameters:
        listener - the ClipboardListener to add.
        See Also:
        ClipboardListener

      • removeClipboardListener

        Parameters:

        See Also:
        ClipboardListener
